title: Yura 75th birthday
subtext:
Dear Yura!
Happy anniversary to you and your entire family!
We wish you a speedy recovery and further achievements.
We are sure that all your friends, graduates of LIAP-1970, colleagues, engineers, scientists and bosses, raised by you over 50 years, users of algorithms and equipment created with your participation and leadership, join these wishes.
Hold on and don't give up.
Zhora, Valya Kaf 22
